能係講下笑<br />\n但呢啲野真係香港人先會大機會講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c1fa87a914c3ada33bfb5eb6a699eb3bab5486","tid":679041,"uid":174418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"媽咪都係開玩笑"},{"pid":"e8429e21d04f273e2206f006913dff49d9fc6b11","tid":679041,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T04:00:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa903127cc2717143c73768dcf89a71521d3c784","tid":679041,"uid":26711,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:21:59.000Z","msg":"一個post已經睇到唔少比連登思想毒害既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a11593eb88b01b373eff628e02208fdf1beeb80","tid":679041,"uid":87428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"做到誠哥先有自己泳池 私樓最多都係會所泳池"},{"pid":"543ece6ecda57be83e9362d16a8416b159514486","tid":679041,"uid":133611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"好明顯係個仔因為細個，要求太不切實際<br />\n我覺得呀媽反應係咁解：<br />\n<br />\n「哇，要泳池咁撚誇張，小朋友唔知錢點賺嘅真係直接，我點撚樣比你啊，唯一機會係你自己嚟啦」<br />\n仲要係講笑mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}